{"updated":1769695209,"is_labeled":false,"copyright_permission":"need_review","settings":{"table_of_contents":{"enabled":false}},"excerpt":"基于对 nccl/src/ 目录的分析，NCCL 采用了分层模块化的架构设计。以下是核心架构要点：一、核心架构分层1. 用户API层 (nccl\\src\\http://collectives.cc )提供标准集合通信接口：AllReduce、AllGather、Broadcast、Reduce、ReduceScatter、Send/Recv数据类型支持：int8-64、uint8-64、float16/32/64、bfloat16、float8封装操作参数并调用 [ncclEnqueueCheck()] (nccl\\src\\include\\enqueue.h) 进入调度层2. 调度与入队层 (nccl\\src\\…","admin_closed_comment":false,"voting":0,"article_type":"normal","reason":"","force_login_when_click_read_more":false,"excerpt_title":"","id":"1970235420945126904","voteup_count":7,"title_image":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-34c23d369c338cc921f1dfad08878d95_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b","has_column":true,"url":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1970235420945126904","comment_permission":"censor","author":{"is_followed":false,"avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-eb249fe9f1461ad37894b3362aa80eb4.jpg?source=d16d100b","uid":"1019697603679793152","user_type":"people","is_following":false,"type":"people","url_token":"changping123","id":"8ffff72080e204609981e6e00fe98684","description":"某Ai芯片公司架构师","name":"常平","is_advertiser":false,"headline":"为学，闻道，践行！","gender":1,"url":"/people/8ffff72080e204609981e6e00fe98684","avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-eb249fe9f1461ad37894b3362aa80eb4_l.jpg?source=d16d100b","is_org":false,"badge":[]},"comment_count":0,"created":1762521780,"content":"<p data-pid=\"Rjgubx_s\">基于对 <code>nccl/src/</code> 目录的分析，NCCL 采用了分层模块化的架构设计。以下是核心架构要点：</p><h3>一、核心架构分层</h3><h3>1. <b>用户API层</b> (nccl\\src\\<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//collectives.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">collectives.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a>)</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"eZ9NzED2\">提供标准集合通信接口：AllReduce、AllGather、Broadcast、Reduce、ReduceScatter、Send/Recv</li><li data-pid=\"zzKh8SOJ\">数据类型支持：int8-64、uint8-64、float16/32/64、bfloat16、float8</li><li data-pid=\"rGJRxM4N\">封装操作参数并调用 [ncclEnqueueCheck()] (nccl\\src\\include\\enqueue.h) 进入调度层</li></ul><h3>2. <b>调度与入队层</b>  (nccl\\src\\<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//enqueue.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">enqueue.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a>)</h3><p data-pid=\"Os9eXSTD\"><b>关键功能</b>：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"pqF0Fx04\"><b>工作批处理</b>：通过 <code>addWorkBatchToPlan()</code> 将多个操作合并</li><li data-pid=\"KVNQJbX8\"><b>内核启动</b>：管理 CUDA 内核参数和执行配置</li><li data-pid=\"JqiowZ8c\"><b>资源规划</b>：分配通道、线程块、共享内存</li><li data-pid=\"tEJO94mY\"><b>Proxy集成</b>：通过 <code>addProxyOpIfNeeded()</code> 添加网络代理操作</li><li data-pid=\"6Z-MRPmy\"><b>核心数据结构</b>：</li></ul><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">ncclKernelPlan</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">threadPerBlock</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">nWorkBatches</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">size_t</span> <span class=\"n\">workBytes</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">ncclDevWorkStorageType</span> <span class=\"n\">workStorageType</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">ncclDevKernelArgs</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">kernelArgs</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">};</span>\n</code></pre></div><h3>3. <b>通信器层</b> (nccl\\src\\include\\comm.h, nccl\\src\\<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//init.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">init.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a>)</h3><p data-pid=\"f04w_nqE\"><b>ncclComm 核心结构</b>：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"BPMEEQ7o\">管理通信器生命周期（初始化、配置、销毁）</li><li data-pid=\"ZD8KI-Mu\">维护拓扑信息和通道配置</li><li data-pid=\"t3HIYsOb\">包含共享资源 ([ncclSharedResources] ( nccl\\src\\include\\comm.h)：</li><ul><li data-pid=\"WnA7-lxj\">Proxy状态</li><li data-pid=\"U0X0uNRO\">GIN（GPU-Initiated Network）状态</li><li data-pid=\"Q_GtnRAw\">内部CUDA流</li><li data-pid=\"tEGdt2ul\">P2P和集合操作计数器</li></ul></ul><h3>4. <b>拓扑层</b> (<code>graph/topo.cc</code> )</h3><p data-pid=\"cR8qQEVu\"><b>设计亮点</b>：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"a2atQ51T\"><b>节点类型</b>：GPU、PCI、NVS（NVSwitch）、CPU、NIC、NET</li><li data-pid=\"Arlof977\"><b>链路类型</b>：LOC、NVL（NVLink）、C2C、PCI、SYS、NET</li><li data-pid=\"9kIOBMmU\"><b>路径类型</b>（11种） (nccl\\src\\graph\\topo.h：</li><ul><li data-pid=\"NaPkctbD\">PATH_NVL：通过 NVLink 直连</li><li data-pid=\"AiMZGob7\">PATH_PIX：单 PCIe 桥接</li><li data-pid=\"9fsygsbw\">PATH_PXB：多 PCIe 桥接</li><li data-pid=\"4BR3D-9C\">PATH_PHB：跨 PCIe Host Bridge</li><li data-pid=\"mIoNEicv\">PATH_SYS：跨 NUMA 节点</li></ul></ul><p data-pid=\"vy2jCLH1\"><b>带宽定义</b>：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"nl\">SM100_NVLINK_BW</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"mf\">40.1</span> <span class=\"n\">GB</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">s</span>\n    <span class=\"nl\">SM90_NVLINK_BW</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"mf\">20.6</span> <span class=\"n\">GB</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">s</span>\n    <span class=\"nl\">SM80_NVLINK_BW</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"mf\">20.0</span> <span class=\"n\">GB</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">s</span>\n    <span class=\"nl\">PCI_BW</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"mf\">12.0</span> <span class=\"n\">GB</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">s</span>\n    <span class=\"nl\">NET_BW</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"mf\">12.0</span> <span class=\"n\">GB</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">s</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">100</span><span class=\"n\">Gbit</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"Yw9tUOxu\"><b>拓扑发现</b>：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"wiK5J2De\">自动检测 GPU、NIC、CPU 拓扑</li><li data-pid=\"1sBqa3l8\">支持 XML 配置覆盖</li><li data-pid=\"XztOMCmA\">计算最优通信路径</li></ul><h3>5. <b>传输层</b> (<code>transport/</code>)</h3><p data-pid=\"GbGXYB0A\">多后端支持：</p><table data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"table\" data-size=\"normal\" data-row-style=\"normal\"><tbody><tr><th>传输方式</th><th>文件</th><th>特性</th></tr><tr><td>InfiniBand</td><td><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//net_ib.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">net_ib.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></td><td>RDMA、GPUDirect、MLX5 加速</td></tr><tr><td>共享内存</td><td><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//shm.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">shm.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></td><td>节点内零拷贝</td></tr><tr><td>TCP Socket</td><td><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//net_socket.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">net_socket.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></td><td>通用网络 fallback</td></tr><tr><td>NVLink SHARP</td><td><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//nvls.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">nvls.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></td><td>NVSwitch 集合加速</td></tr><tr><td>P2P</td><td><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//p2p.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">p2p.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></td><td>GPU间直连</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>6. <b>设备层</b> (<code>device/</code>)</h3><p data-pid=\"irUe4CCD\"><b>内核生成系统</b> ([generate.py] (nccl\\src\\device\\generate.py)：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"pIwnOcrr\"><b>算法</b>：TREE、RING、COLLNET、NVLS</li><li data-pid=\"u3ACZYyy\"><b>协议</b>：LL（低延迟）、LL128、SIMPLE（高带宽）</li><li data-pid=\"K43kBDgk\"><b>优化原语</b> ：</li><ul><li data-pid=\"NdY27Lub\">nccl\\src\\device\\prims_ll.h：低延迟原语</li><li data-pid=\"7lV6wTkJ\">nccl\\src\\device\\prims_ll128.h：128位对齐优化</li><li data-pid=\"RYLyo5nN\">nccl\\src\\device\\prims_simple.h：简单协议主实现</li></ul><li data-pid=\"lwOVBS9D\"><b>集合内核</b>：</li></ul><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"n\">all_reduce</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">h</span>  <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">AllReduce</span> <span class=\"err\">优化</span>\n<span class=\"n\">reduce_kernel</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">h</span>  <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">Reduce</span> <span class=\"err\">操作</span>\n<span class=\"n\">all_gather</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">h</span>  <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">AllGather</span> <span class=\"err\">实现</span>\n<span class=\"n\">reduce_scatter</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">h</span>  <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">ReduceScatter</span>\n</code></pre></div><h3>7. <b>代理层</b> (nccl\\src\\<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//proxy.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">proxy.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a>)</h3><p data-pid=\"JreJAezx\"><b>异步网络引擎</b>：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"AD7uLSkc\">专用 CPU 线程处理网络 I/O</li><li data-pid=\"_Ic-cGVn\">GPU 计算与网络通信重叠</li><li data-pid=\"cwYu2QPg\">连接管理和流控</li><li data-pid=\"GmqNjjlv\">支持预期响应队列 ([ncclExpectedProxyResponse] (nccl\\src\\include\\proxy.h)</li></ul><h3>二、关键数据流</h3><h3>集合通信调用流程：</h3><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">用户调用 ncclAllReduce()\n ↓\ncollectives.cc: 参数封装为 ncclInfo\n ↓\nenqueue.cc: ncclEnqueueCheck()\n ↓\n工作批处理与规划\n ↓\n设备内核启动 + Proxy操作入队\n ↓\ndevice/: GPU执行集合内核\n ↓\ntransport/: 网络传输（IB/Socket/SHM）\n ↓\nproxy.cc: 异步网络进度管理</code></pre></div><h3>初始化流程：</h3><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">ncclGetUniqueId()\n ↓\nbootstrap.cc: 建立初始通信\n ↓\ninit.cc: ncclCommInitRank()\n ↓\ngraph/topo.cc: 拓扑检测\n ├─ GPU 检测（NVML）\n ├─ NIC 检测（插件）\n └─ 路径计算\n ↓\nchannel.cc: 通道分配\n ↓\ntransport/: 传输层初始化\n ↓\ndevice/: 内核加载与配置</code></pre></div><h3>三、高级特性</h3><h3>1. <b>算法自动选择</b> (<code>graph/tuning.cc</code>)</h3><p data-pid=\"EWNTbUrT\">根据：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"IpXqweuV\">消息大小</li><li data-pid=\"mLpr2jIs\">节点数量</li><li data-pid=\"V3ugGrav\">拓扑结构</li><li data-pid=\"IAG76qNa\">网络特性</li><li data-pid=\"VvVIP6Gc\">动态选择 RING/TREE/COLLNET/NVLS</li></ul><h3>2. <b>内存注册</b> (<code>register/</code>)</h3><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">集合注册 ([coll_reg.cc] (nccl\\src\\register\\coll_reg.cc)：批量缓冲区注册\nP2P注册 ([sendrecv_reg.cc] (\\nccl\\src\\register\\sendrecv_reg.cc)：点对点零拷贝</code></pre></div><h3>3. <b>对称内存</b> (<code>scheduler/symmetric_sched.cc</code>)</h3><p data-pid=\"THqwHnxs\">GPU间对称分配内存，优化多GPU通信</p><h3>4. <b>插件系统</b> (<code>plugin/</code>)</h3><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">plugin_open.cc   \n├─ net/ 网络后端插件   \n├─ tuner/ 算法调优插件   \n├─ profiler/ 性能分析插件   \n└─ env/ 环境管理插件</code></pre></div><h3>5. <b>RAS支持</b> (<code>ras/</code>)</h3><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">client_support.cc)：客户端支持\nrasnet.cc：网络错误检测\ncollectives.cc：集合操作验证\npeers.cc：对等连接监控</code></pre></div><h3>6. <b>GIN - GPU发起网络</b> (<code>gin/</code>)</h3><p data-pid=\"4AjwQo3Y\">允许GPU直接发起网络操作，减少CPU介入</p><h3>四、优化技术</h3><h3>1. <b>多协议支持</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"eJNEhERd\"><b>LL</b>：小消息（&lt;128KB），低延迟</li><li data-pid=\"cclrt0Rz\"><b>LL128</b>：128位对齐，平衡性能</li><li data-pid=\"0iQAGaG1\"><b>SIMPLE</b>：大消息（&gt;1MB），高带宽</li></ul><h3>2. <b>通道并行</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"aGrikqKx\">最多32个通道并行传输</li><li data-pid=\"AyFgiNE9\">每通道独立 [ncclChannel] (nccl\\src\\include\\comm.h) 结构</li><li data-pid=\"MwxxiWai\">Ring/Tree 独立配置</li></ul><h3>3. <b>工作批处理</b></h3><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">struct ncclDevWorkBatch {  \nuint8_t workType;   \nuint8_t funcId;   \nuint32_t offsetBase;   \nuint64_t offsetBitset;   \n};</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"YslooCED\">减少内核启动开销</p><h3>4. <b>零拷贝优化</b></h3><ul><li data-pid=\"DlATUsvy\">GPUDirect RDMA [nccl\\src\\misc\\<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//gdrwrap.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">gdrwrap.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a>]</li><li data-pid=\"5kA5vvY7\">共享内存传输</li><li data-pid=\"Yajka6UL\">用户缓冲区注册</li></ul><h3>五、硬件抽象层 (<code>misc/</code>)</h3><table data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"table\" data-size=\"normal\" data-row-style=\"normal\"><tbody><tr><th>包装器</th><th>目标API</th><th>功能</th></tr><tr><td>[<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//cudawrap.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">cudawrap.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a>]</td><td>CUDA Runtime</td><td>GPU操作</td></tr><tr><td>[<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//nvmlwrap.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">nvmlwrap.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a>]</td><td>NVML</td><td>GPU管理</td></tr><tr><td>[<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//ibvwrap.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">ibvwrap.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a>]</td><td>Verbs</td><td>InfiniBand</td></tr><tr><td>[<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//gdrwrap.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">gdrwrap.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a>]</td><td>GDRCopy</td><td>GPUDirect</td></tr><tr><td>[<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//mlx5dvwrap.cc\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">mlx5dvwrap.cc</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a>]</td><td>MLX5 DevX</td><td>Mellanox加速</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>六、编译系统</h3><h3>CMake 构建目标：</h3><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-cmake\"><span class=\"err\">libnccl.so</span> <span class=\"c\"># 共享库\n</span><span class=\"c\"></span><span class=\"err\">libnccl_static.a</span> <span class=\"c\"># 静态库\n</span><span class=\"c\"></span><span class=\"err\">ncclras</span> <span class=\"err\">#</span> <span class=\"err\">RAS客户端</span></code></pre></div><h3>内核生成：</h3><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">generate.py → 生成设备内核组合\n支持过滤：ONLY_FUNCS<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&#34;AllReduce Sum f32 RING LL128&#34;</span></code></pre></div><h3>总结</h3><p data-pid=\"EMgt4pXj\">NCCL 架构核心优势：</p><ol><li data-pid=\"Xuf5GkK3\"><b>分层设计</b>：清晰的API、调度、传输、设备分离</li><li data-pid=\"dRPpKYaL\"><b>拓扑感知</b>：自动检测并优化通信路径</li><li data-pid=\"J2nRo850\"><b>多后端支持</b>：IB、TCP、SHM、NVLink无缝切换</li><li data-pid=\"RxKE7hR2\"><b>性能优化</b>：多协议、零拷贝、异步代理</li><li data-pid=\"cqVralLR\"><b>可扩展性</b>：插件系统支持自定义扩展</li><li data-pid=\"QVuueC7b\"><b>高可靠性</b>：完整的RAS错误处理</li></ol><h2>版权申明</h2><p data-pid=\"SvTFVz-p\">本文的版权协议为 CC-BY-NC-ND license：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0/deed.zh\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">creativecommons.org/lic</span><span class=\"invisible\">enses/by-nc-nd/3.0/deed.zh</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"1brbrZ5Z\">在遵循署名、非商业使用（以获利为准）以及禁止演绎的前提下可以自由阅读、分享、转发、复制、分发等。</p>","state":"published","content_need_truncated":true,"image_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-34c23d369c338cc921f1dfad08878d95_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b","title":"第10篇 - 集合通信 - NCCL 代码架构解析","can_comment":{"status":true,"reason":"请输入评论，您的评论将会由作者筛选后显示"},"type":"article","suggest_edit":{"status":false,"url":"","reason":"","tip":"","title":""}}
